### **SPDR S&P/ASX 50 ETF (SFY) – Distribution Announcement Summary**

- **Distribution Reinvestment Plan (DRP)**: Active, reinvestment unless opted for cash. Changes must be submitted by **30 June 2025**.  

No material capital structure or liquidity-impacting changes identified.
